Customer-Centric Approach: Our clients' needs are at the forefront of everything we do. We strive to provide tailored solutions and exceptional service that surpass expectations. Expertise: Our team of knowledgeable professionals possesses a deep understanding of EOL hardware, allowing us to offer expert guidance and support to our clients. Innovation: We continually explore emerging technologies and industry trends to provide our clients with the most advanced EOL solutions available. Consulting and Support: Our team of experts offers consulting services to help clients choose the right EOL parts and solutions for their specific requirements. We provide ongoing support to ensure optimal performance and reliability. Hardware Maintenance: We offer maintenance and repair services for EOL hardware, extending its lifespan and reducing the total cost of ownership for our clients. Custom Solutions: We design and build customized EOL hardware solutions to meet unique business needs, maximizing performance and efficiency. Sustainability Initiatives: Server Solutions actively promotes sustainability by facilitating the responsible disposal and recycling of retired IT equipment. Why Choose Server Solutions: Quality Assurance:  We rigorously test and certify all EOL hardware to guarantee its performance and reliability. Cost Efficiency: Our EOL solutions provide a cost-effective alternative to purchasing new equipment, allowing businesses to allocate resources more efficiently. Sustainability Commitment:  By choosing Server Solutions, clients contribute to reducing electronic waste and promoting environmental sustainability. Expert Guidance:  Our experienced team of professionals is always ready to assist clients in making informed decisions and optimizing their IT infrastructure. Global Reach:  We serve clients globally, offering seamless access to our EOL hardware solutions regardless of location. At Server Solutions, we are dedicated to transforming the way businesses approach IT hardware lifecycle management. By choosing us as your EOL hardware partner, you are not only extending the life of your IT infrastructure but also contributing to a more sustainable and responsible tech industry.

Description: We are digitizing industries in blockchain to create a better world.
Full Description: We are digitizing industries to create a better world. A world with new opportunities for people to evolve and enjoy their lives. A new way of working, investing, creating business and opportunities for all sectors. Let me tell you more about our work: Since the inception of blockchain, we have championed its application across all sectors as Codebooster. What started as an experiment that took place exclusively online is now changing industries and transforming the way they work forever. Blockchain technology was first introduced to the world in 2008. It is known as the technology behind cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum. But blockchain offers more. Much more. We believe blockchain can revolutionize data management by decentralizing information storage, increasing process efficiency and, at the same time, ensuring greater security for everything from IoT (Internet of Things) devices to health records, supply chains and even government agencies. That means we have another step to go. Let me give you an example about our work with this new vision: The cannabis industry's transition to using this revolutionary technology has benefited greatly from our work with them by making it possible to conduct transactions at low cost rather than the high cost and risk of using large amounts of cash. This works through a system where data is automatically shared across devices without any human intervention, ultimately leading to transparency within these markets no longer being compromised thanks in large part to their use of distributed ledger technology: the Orion Project, also known as WID Token, is our vision for this industry, and we are already working with our own cryptocurrency, its own payment gateway and DAPP marketplace. My company has been looking at getting rid of its old concept, because didn't reflect how far the technology had come since its inception. That's why we are rebranding, so the community can see us in a new light: a more modern take on how you all have been operating for years and now it's time to step up our game! We want to show the community that we are all in this together. We need each other's help, and there is no better way to show our gratitude than through a rebranding that reflects our new perspective of life as one big ecosystem, made up of industries (Constellations) and groups within each constellation, which reference different processes within the industry that need to be optimized or changed to increase the quality of life in our communities. Say hello to Clusterfy, our new name that will replicate the world we see in front of us. Soon you will be able to visit www.clusterfy.io! Sincerely, Andrés Galmez Clusterfy Owner
Headquarters Regions: Greater Miami Area, East Coast, Southern US

Description: Altr Coin uses blockchain technology to reduce currency fluctuations and transfer fees in the global money transfer market.
Full Description: Around the world, there are billions of people living in emerging markets who have to transfer funds in and out of various markets.  Altr Coin seeks to end costly transfer fees and exchange rates and replace them with a seamless new cryptocurrency that eliminates fluctuations and reduces costly transfer fees.  Unlike traditional cryptocurrencies, Altr Coin is built with the focus of increasing transactional value via P2P and B2B transactions and has the organizational structure to support this effort.  Altr Coin will limit the number of initial coins available to the public, thereby maintaining a low volume of coins available as well as a high cost per coin.  This will prevent volatile swings in Altr Coin value, making Altr Coin ideal for transactions due to the reduced downside risk.   Altr Coin has a dedicated team of investors and partners from various industries with the shared focus of executing strategic partnerships that will enhance the value of Altr Coin by increasing the volume of transactions. Furthermore, the Altr Coin team is dedicated to maintaining full transparency with the Altr Coin community to build long term value and confidence.

Description: TWI offers innovative healthcare technology solutions, combining advanced APIs and apps to enhance patient care and healthcare management.
Full Description: Total Wellness Innovations Inc. (TWI) leads the forefront of healthcare technology with our comprehensive Whole You mobile and web app, designed to revolutionize patient engagement and healthcare management. Whole You seamlessly integrates advanced technological solutions, including our proprietary APIs, to provide a customized, user-friendly, and efficient health management experience. Whole You is the embodiment of our vision, combining Electronic Health Records (EHRs) workflows with an intuitive user interface. It leverages the power of our APIs to deliver a holistic health management platform. This integration facilitates a more connected and personalized healthcare experience, making it easier for patients to manage their health and for healthcare providers to deliver optimal care. Our Medical Content Library API forms a crucial part of Whole You, serving as a centralized repository of evidence-based, medically reviewed content. It empowers patients with reliable and accessible medical information, enhancing their understanding and engagement with their health. In Whole You, this API provides users with a wealth of information at their fingertips, aiding in informed decision-making and patient education. The Patient Tracker API is another integral component of Whole You. It provides real-time tracking for key aspects of a patient's medical workflow, such as hydration, medication, nutrition, and exercise. This API ensures that all pertinent health data is up-to-date and easily accessible within the Whole You platform, enabling continuous monitoring and more effective health management. Lastly, our Clinical Translator API is pivotal in transforming unstructured and structured medical data into actionable insights. Within Whole You, it takes raw clinical information from EHRs and other medical documents and turns it into comprehensible Activities & Goals tailored to each patient's unique needs. This functionality is crucial for personalizing the healthcare experience and making complex medical data understandable and actionable for both patients and healthcare providers. At Total Wellness Innovations Inc., Whole You stands as a testament to our dedication to enhancing healthcare management through technology. By integrating our advanced APIs into this comprehensive platform, we are making strides in empowering patients, simplifying healthcare workflows, and paving the way for a more informed and engaged approach to health and wellness.
